Distance: 1500 meters Conditions: 9-11 mph cross-headwind, with gusts up to 30 mph. Despite the wind, the water was relatively good with slight chop in the first 500 and final 150. Comments: Many thanks to Tabor for making the trip today!
SPS girls 3rd and 4th boats rowed an exhibition race. G4 started roughly 30 meters over the line; G3 started about 5 meters over.
